---
import SectionHeader from "./SectionHeader.astro";
import SkillsGrid from "./SkillsGrid.astro";

const heading = "About";
---

<section id="about" class="py-12 px-4">
  <div class="space-y-8">
    <SectionHeader heading={heading} />
    <div class="space-y-6">
      <p>I build responsive, dynamic web apps with <span class="text-ash-grey font-medium">Astro</span>, <span class="text-ash-grey font-medium">TailwindCSS</span> and <span class="text-ash-grey font-medium">React</span>—focusing on clean code, intuitive design, and great user experiences.</p>
      <p>Eager to contribute to dynamic projects while continuously expanding my skills in building scalable and responsive web applications.</p>
      <p>When I'm not deep in development mode, you'll either find me on the tennis court, running along scenic trails, or enjoying a well-earned rest day—while humbly accepting that my pets are the true project managers at home.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="space-y-5">
      <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-sans font-medium">My Skills</h3>
      <p>I'm a passionate learner and these are some of the technologies and tools I've used often. </p>
      <SkillsGrid />
    </div>
  </div>
  <!-- <div class="py-6 px-4 space-y-4 md:py-8 md:mx-4 md:px-6 bg-linear-to-t from-slate-950 to-sky-700/20 md:rounded-2xl md:shadow-xl"> -->
</section>
